    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Egmundella grimaldii Leloup, 1940. a–c, stn GR-50; a, part of rhizocaulomic hydrorhiza with hydrothecae and nematothecae; b, hydrothecae; c, nematothecae. d–e, stn MO263; d, part of rhizocaulomic hydrorhiza with hydrotheca and nematothecae; e, gonotheca on hydrorhiza. Scale bar: a = 0.5 mm; b = 1 mm; c = 0.2 mm; d–e = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7836970/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7836974>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Egmundella grimaldii Leloup, 1940. a–c, stn MO263, a, frontal view of a gonotheca; b, lateral view of (the same) gonotheca and some nematothecae on hydrorhiza; c, lateral view of gonotheca, detail of longitudinal ridges. Scale bar: a–c = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7836974/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

